704616f-a.title: Brooklyn: Georgia Avenue - Glenmore Avenue
704616f-a.text:
Georgia Ave., between Glenmore and Liberty Aves., showing at the right,
a section of Piel Bros. Beverage Mfg. Co. This is a view north.
April 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
